<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF446AFBFF8594011A47B992" pageId="191" pageNumber="953" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF446AFBFF8594011A47B992" blockId="191.[119,1328,284,755]" pageId="191" pageNumber="953">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF446AFBFF8594011FDCB94B" bold="true" box="[121,476,600,633]" pageId="191" pageNumber="953">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Morris’s 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF446AFBFF8694261ED4B992" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[122,212,639,672]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="191" pageNumber="953" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
